      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:7:6:2",
      "text": [
        " رَأَيْتُ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ ( عليه السلام ) وَ هُوَ يَشْرَبُ فِي قَدَحٍ مِنْ خَزَفٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Abu Ali Al Ashary, from Muhammad Bin Abdul Jabbar, from Muhammad Bin Salim, from Ahmad Bin Al Nazar, from Amro Bin Abu Al Miqdam who said, ",
          "‘I saw Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> and he<sup>asws</sup> was drinking in a ceramic cup’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Abu Ali al-Ash‘ariy has narrated from Muhammad ibn ‘Abd al-Jabbar from Muhammad ibn Salim from Ahmad ibn abu al-Nadr from ‘Amr ibn abu al-Miqdam who has said the following: “I saw abu Ja’far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, drink water from a pottery bowl.’” "
        ]
      }
    },
